pan style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日826 仲有國泰城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98792d40e4713e386ac52102db0449bb7db3eb56","tid":1503684,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"e885e7ba7c408f458f909cc0a8f9059f01080cdd","tid":1503684,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a416024083b1504e27737e9f1437c011f0e4a9b","tid":1503684,"uid":438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"唔食豬駛死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同班柒頭做節一定要食雞一樣唔識變通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"何不食肉糜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地冇得揀 本身最平就係豬"},{"pid":"49720793725e0b5e85acbf5b73a99ab91e567091","tid":1503684,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"仲有兩腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蝗女大奶"}]}